variable {D : Type u‚ÇÇ} [Category.{v‚ÇÇ} D]

/-- Reinterpreting an `F`-structured arrow `X ‚ü∂ F.obj d` as an arrow under `X` induces a functor
    `StructuredArrow X F ‚•§ Under X`. -/
@[simps!]
